<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>EMA515_03_SU_0004_s</title>

  <!-- 공통 js-->
  <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

  <!-- 공통 css-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

  <!-- 개별 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema515_03.css" />
</head>

<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema515_03_su_0004">
    <section class="title type2 fraction_title">
      <h2 data-head="2" class="fraction_box_title">
        <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
          <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
            <div class="fraction_box ml_0">
              <span>7</span>
              <span>10</span>
            </div>
            +
            <div class="fraction_box ml_2">
              <span>5</span>
              <span>12</span>
            </div>
            를 어떻게 계산하는지 알아봅시다.
          </div>
        </div>
      </h2>
    </section>

    <section class="contents paging_layout">
      <div class="input_area">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">두 분모의 곱을 공통분모로 하여 통분한 후 계산해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="container_515">
              <div class="operations_column">
                <div class="operations">
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>7</span>
                    <span>10</span>
                  </div>
                  +
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>5</span>
                    <span>12</span>
                  </div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>7×12</span>
                    <span>10×12</span>
                  </div>
                  +
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>
                      5×
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="10"></math-field>
                      </div>
                    </span>
                    <span>12×10</span>
                  </div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>84</span>
                    <span>120</span>
                  </div>
                  +
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="50"></math-field>
                      </div>
                    </span>
                    <span>120</span>
                  </div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="134"></math-field>
                      </div>
                    </span>
                    <span>120</span>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="operations">
                  =
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span>
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="24"></math-field>
                      </div>
                    </span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="14"></math-field>
                        </div>
                      </span>
                      <span>120</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  =
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span>
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="24"></math-field>
                      </div>
                    </span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                        </div>
                      </span>
                      <span>120</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">두 분모의 최소공배수를 공통분모로 하여 통분한 후 계산해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="container_515">
              <div class="operations">
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>7</span>
                  <span>10</span>
                </div>
                +
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>5</span>
                  <span>12</span>
                </div>
                =
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>7×6</span>
                  <span>10×6</span>
                </div>
                +
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>
                    5×
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="5"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </span>
                  <span>12×
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="5"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </span>
                </div>
                =
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>42</span>
                  <span>60</span>
                </div>
                +
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="25"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </span>
                  <span>60</span>
                </div>
                =
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="67"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </span>
                  <span>60</span>
                </div>
                =
                <div class="mixed_fraction">
                  <span>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </span>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                      </div>
                    </span>
                    <span>60</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_3">
          <h3 lang="y">분모가 다른 진분수의 덧셈하는 방법을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
              <div class="example_box">
                <p lang="y">두 분모의 곱이나 최소공배수를 공통분모로 하여 통분한 후 분모는 그대로 쓰고 분자끼리 더합니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="btn_area">
        <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
        <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
        <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>

</html>